{"tid":2038041,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"全球黃色經濟圈第一波：阻止中資上市","createTime":"2020-05-27T10:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T15:22:55.000Z","uid":113435,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7b679266f6f92c6aa02d6af673580f8ad5c4b1","tid":2038041,"uid":113435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"開口都有講，「知己知彼，百戰百勝」。面對中共強大的勢力，香港人要抵抗，不能靠蠻力，只能智取。<br />\n<br />\n係出謀獻策前，我想大家了解兩件最近發生的事。<br />\n<br />\n1. 中美貿易戰<br />\n中美貿易戰2018年開打，直至2020年頭暫時結束。中國跪低，簽署「第一階段貿易協議」。<br />\n<br />\n中國同意未來2年增購2,000億美元的美國商品和務服，主要集中在製造業、能源、農業和服務業方面，其中包括320億美元農產品。<br />\n<br />\n條款明顯對中國不利，但由於關稅影響經濟，中共被迫跪低。<br />\n<br />\n結論：中國實行「戰狼外交」，但如果嚴重影響經濟，都有可能跪底。<br />\n<br />\n2. 瑞幸咖啡「做假」被勒令退市<br />\n中資「瑞幸咖啡」造假數，被香港踢爆，美國勒令退市。<br />\n詳情<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200405/Z27NF2BYU63JI7VZGNV2UGI3NQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200405%2FZ27NF2BYU63JI7VZGNV2UGI3NQ%2F&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32csFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=a9a96e70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200405%2FZ27NF2BYU63JI7VZGNV2UGI3NQ%2F&h=4ff410c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200405/Z27NF2BYU63JI7VZGNV2UGI3NQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n結論：中資上市，香港嘅影響力係非常大。<br />\n<br />\n我們再分析現時香港的優勢<br />\n<br />\n1. 審計制度與國際接軌<br />\n<br />\n2. 資訊自由流通（暫時）<br />\n<br />\n3. 鄰近中國地區，方便往返<br />\n<br />\n4. 熟悉中國語言、經濟、社會狀況<br />\n<br />\n所以，我們應該從「瑞幸咖啡造假」這件事學習，如何利用香港的優勢，阻止中資到香港、美國、世界各地上市。<br />\n<br />\n中資企業融資難度大增，我們就唔需用任何暴力，就足以摧毀中國經濟。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔需要係金融界的專業人士，只需要抱住一副懷疑的心，對中資企業打破沙盤問到篤，甚至返大陸親身視察，搜集企業造假證據，以中資企業的鬆散管理，很容易便找到漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n搵到證據，便利用香港的資訊自由，向全球發佈，務求成功阻止中資係香港或者外國融資上市。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUG9OjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUG9OjG.jpg&h=265f96b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22fb08f2866bb7a1e34b9de73547b6d2bf6b377e","tid":2038041,"uid":208722,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:13:18.000Z","msg":"大喜屋都認購不足上唔到市，而家真係槍打出頭鳥，邊個上邊個死"},{"pid":"aee47f9a45e174d228c94370462782636b9c593d","tid":2038041,"uid":228794,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:15:15.000Z","msg":"咁京東大家抽唔抽 ？"},{"pid":"af459193db64f2ee7a4c7f3238ac5ff637bfd029","tid":2038041,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"[文宣方向][跳出同溫層]民意調查分析<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2037458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2037458</a>"},{"pid":"e154fdb89dd417ce0fe9310592b1e2feb3cfe52f","tid":2038041,"uid":113435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tYdgtnU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtYdgtnU.jpg&h=0c1ce3a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9925c7d4941ffc566515e29d2d2af9d37acffe3","tid":2038041,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d23c974764afa7601c2bf55fdcf0c141aa72897","tid":2038041,"uid":283152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:23:03.000Z","msg":"香港明明揸住中國嘅春袋 咁多auditor 律師 banker等等幫手上市 知又知得最多 但偏偏咁耐以黎連少少八卦野都爆唔到出黎 我就唔信瑞幸係唯一一間做假數嘅中國企業"},{"pid":"637bfec38584eebc1062c8344f926ac9d5d2e76a","tid":2038041,"uid":34348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aee47f9a45e174d228c94370462782636b9c593d","tid":2038041,"uid":228794,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:15:15.000Z","msg":"咁京東大家抽唔抽 ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:25:24.000Z","msg":"無錢，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e959ae83ac0aabb08e0cc9d3c32f1f5936ab2e38","tid":2038041,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:27:21.000Z","msg":"睇唔明 但我照推"},{